    <!-- Slide 5: Modern Influence -->
    <div id="slide5" class="slide">
        <div class="slide-content">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800">Boole's Enduring Legacy</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Boole's work is not just a historical footnote; it is the fundamental "language" of computing. Every smartphone, computer, and network router relies on logic gates that perform Boolean operations. This foundation extends directly into the world of Artificial Intelligence, where complex algorithms and neural networks are built upon millions of simple binary decisions.</p>
            <div class="flex justify-center">
                <img src="https://placehold.co/600x300/4f46e5/FFFFFF?text=Modern+Circuit+Board" alt="Close-up of a modern circuit board" class="rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mt-4">In a fascinating twist of history, Boole's great-great-grandson, renowned computer scientist <strong>Geoffrey Hinton</strong>, became one of the "godfathers of AI" through his pioneering work on deep learning. Hinton's work, which has revolutionized the field, is a direct continuation of the logical tradition started by his ancestor, George Boole.</p>
            <a href="https://georgeboole.com/boole/life/ucc/lawsofthought/" target="_blank" class="nav-button bg-purple-600 text-white mt-4 inline-flex">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
